  "datePublished": "2025-12-23",
  "description": "Before beginning, I want to say that this piece is for, mostly, adult cishet white men. I understand that many folk need to lie through the Holidays for their own safety, and I don\u0026rsquo;t want them to read this and get any idea that the reasons I give here are a good enough reason to put your safety on the line. But if it\u0026rsquo;s not safety, and you just don\u0026rsquo;t like to make noise at Christmas Dinner? Then this is for you.\n",
  "name": "This Christmas, give yourself bravery",
